      <title>DigiCert 的 Sinha 谈业务展望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-31/digicert-s-sinha-on-business-outlook-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[DigiCert 首席执行官 Amit Sinha 讨论了他对公司业务和数字安全领域的展望，因为量子计算和生成式人工智能等技术创新带来了越来越多的数字信任问题。他在“Daybreak Australia”节目中与 Annabelle Droulers 和 Haidi Stroud-Watts 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-31/digicert-s-sinha-on-business-outlook-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 03:06:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
